'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2915] on 12 November 2000 at 11:47:05 am'!"Change Set:		230ExplorerString-smaDate:			12 November 2000Author:			Stefan Matthias AustThis implements the compromise Doug Way and Bob Arning (sort of) worked out regarding asString/printString in the object explorer.  As the explorer is mainly a programmer's tool, I agree with Doug that it should use printString as default."!!Object methodsFor: 'user interface' stamp: 'sma 11/12/2000 11:43'!asExplorerString	^ self printString! !!ObjectExplorerWrapper methodsFor: 'converting' stamp: 'sma 11/12/2000 11:45'!asString	| string |	string _ itemName , ': ' , item asExplorerString.	(string includes: Character cr)		ifTrue: [^ string withSeparatorsCompacted].	^ string! !!String methodsFor: 'user interface' stamp: 'sma 11/12/2000 11:44'!asExplorerString	^ self asString! !!Symbol methodsFor: 'user interface' stamp: 'sma 11/12/2000 11:46'!asExplorerString	^ self printString! !ByteArray removeSelector: #asExplorerString!